Length Constraints: Minimum length of 1. Maximum length of 128.  
Pattern: `.*\S.*`   
Required: Yes

 ** [Name](#API_wafRegional_CreateSqlInjectionMatchSet_RequestSyntax) **   <a name="WAF-wafRegional_CreateSqlInjectionMatchSet-request-Name"></a>
A friendly name or description for the [SqlInjectionMatchSet](API_wafRegional_SqlInjectionMatchSet.md) that you're creating. You can't change `Name` after you create the `SqlInjectionMatchSet`.  
Type: String  
Length Constraints: Minimum length of 1. Maximum length of 128.  
Pattern: `.*\S.*`   
Required: Yes

